public class IOPortOperStatusAlarm
extends TTOperStatusAlarm

IOPortOperStatusAlarm extends the TTOperStatusAlarm class. Its receipt signals a change in the operational status of a Reader's IO Port. The abstract model's IOPort.operStatusAlarmControl data element controls the triggering of alarms of this type.
